<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <% include ../views/partials/head %>
    <% include ../views/partials/ga %>

    <title><%= title %></title>
  </head>

  <body>
    
    <!-- Page Content -->
    <% include ../views/partials/navigation %>
    <% include ../views/partials/header %>
    <div class="container">
      
        <!-- Call to Action Well -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="well text-center">
                    Blogwith aims to integrate note taking applications to Wordpress. The goal is to allow users to publish content straight from their favorite note taking applications and not waste time switching between applications.
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- /.col-lg-12 -->
        </div>
        <!-- /.row -->

        <!-- Content Row -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Why Blogwith?</h2>
                <p>If you write in Evernote, Simplenote or Onenote regularly and is looking for a service that allows you to publish straight to the different publishing platform, this is it. Think buffer for writing.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/">More Info</a>
            </div>
            <!-- /.col-md-4 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Note Editors</h2>
                <p>Currently, the connected note editor is Evernote. In the next few releases, Simplenote and Onenote connection will be added.</p>
                <a href="#"><button type="button" class="btn btn-default" disabled>Coming soon</button></a>
            </div>
            <!-- /.col-md-4 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Publishing Platforms</h2>
                <p>Wordpress integration is already available. The next integration will be Tumblr followed by Ghost.</p>
                <a href="#"><button type="button" class="btn btn-default" disabled>Coming soon</button></a>
            </div>
            <!-- /.col-md-4 -->
        </div>
        <!-- /.row -->

        <hr>
    </div>
    <% include ../views/partials/footer %>
  </body>
</html>

